---
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="container px-6 mx-auto">

    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <p class="text-bright-blue text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">The Loop</p>
      <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Four steps. Runs itself.</h2>
      <p class="text-accessible-gray">
        Amplifly isn't a to-do list app or a habit tracker. It's a feedback loop that gets
        smarter the more you use it — without you doing extra work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      {[
        {
          step: '01',
          title: 'Check your brain',
          desc: 'Each morning, pick the state that matches how your brain feels today — Sharp, Spicy, Flat, Foggy, or Scattered. Takes five seconds.',
          icon: '🧠',
        },
        {
          step: '02',
          title: 'Get matched techniques',
          desc: 'Amplifly\'s on-device recommender suggests the conditions most likely to work for your current state — then learns from your feedback.',
          icon: '🎯',
        },
        {
          step: '03',
          title: 'Log your sessions',
          desc: 'After deep work, log how long, how locked-in you were, what helped, and what drained you. 60 seconds.',
          icon: '📝',
        },
        {
          step: '04',
          title: 'Your manual builds',
          desc: 'Over time, the Manual tab fills in: your best hours, your top helpers, your highest-flow brain states, what the recommender has learned.',
          icon: '📖',
        },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="relative bg-soft-blue rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">{item.icon}</div>
          <div class="text-bright-blue text-xs font-bold tracking-widest mb-2">{item.step}</div>
          <h3 class="text-deep-navy font-bold text-lg mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-accessible-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/#waitlist"
         class="inline-block bg-deep-navy hover:bg-navy-light text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors text-base">
        Get Early Access
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
